reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Tons of goodies! Super cute...
reviews.reviewText: Such cute stationery goodies! The quality is decent enough, but certain items look better than others. Unfortunately the print job on the pencil case was done quite poorly and sort of fades away on the edges, looking odd and incomplete. Also, my notebook came with a stubborn bend across the bottom two inches, which stinks, although I guess that could have happened during transport. But anyway, those negatives aside, the rest of the items are just what you'd hope for. My favorites are the pins and the stickers, but it's all good! If you bought all this stuff in a little gift shop, it would definitely cost more than this price. Recommended if you love Cinnamoroll, and if you don't mind the pencil case looking a bit off ~

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love this set!
reviews.reviewText: This is a great set of Cinnamoroll stationery supplies! You get TWO very nice enamel pins, plus a notebook, a bunch of cute stickers, an eraser set, pens, a charm, two pads of sticky notes, a zippered pouch, and a badge holder. The only reason I'm giving this four stars instead of five is that it didn't come with the lanyard itself like it was supposed to. Which doesn't really bother me (I'm not a lanyard fan), but it's something to be aware of. Still very happy with this set and highly recommend it!
